Martin Lamotte https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Lamotte 0 Martin Lamotte (born 2 June 1947) is a French actor, comedian and director. He participated in several films alongside Le Splendid. He is most known for his role on the TV Series "SoeurThérèse.com" and "Nos chers voisins". Martin_Lamotte ( born 2_June_1947 ) is a_French_actor , comedian_and_director .
